            <h2 id="about">Who's behind this?</h2>
            <p><span class="otr">Off The Record</span> is an experimental project by <a href="http://mattandrews.info">Matt Andrews</a>, a music loving web developer. While it's far from the first event of its kind, we wanted to create something where people could make time for good music and hear people talk passionately about why it's great.</p>
